snippet.textDisplay:
Kevain tenu mei dikhaawan
How can I unveil this to you?
Dillon russ gayi aan chaawaan
My heart can find no peace
Teri yaadan ich bikhra mein, dunya sajaawaan
Shattered in your memory, I adorn my world
verse

Sunn ve mein kithay jaawaan
Tell me now, which way do I turn
Hun russ gayi aan raawaan
The roads have disappeared on me
Mei te dassiya si, khwaabaan ich takya si
I feared this would happen
Le hun din v nai chariya
Now the day hasn't even dawned
verse

Te dil ich toon
And my heart is flooded with your memories
Meray mann ich toon
You're my deepest longing
Jaddon vi nai hondi paas
When you're not near
Te tarapdi ay rooh
My soul is in agony
verse

Te ravein tu kareeb sohni, haali na tu ja
Stay close to me, my love don't leave me already
Tu hi hai mera naseeb
You are my destiny
Kaddi vi na jaavein door
Never go far from me
Assi laa dittay jinnay vi tu mangdi ay taaray
When you asked, I gathered all the stars for you
verse

Meri jaan kaddi vi na darri meray pyaaray
You need never fear my love
Dil ich tu
You dwell within my heart
Meri hasrat ay tu
You alone are my yearning
Assi teray uttay marday ne, sunday nai kyu
Don't you see, I'd die for you, why won't you hear me?
pre-chorus

Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday
With each day, my longing for you grows
Teray husn uttay marday assi roz
Each day, your beauty leaves me more undone
Ki kariye sajna bol
Tell me how to survive, my love
Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray
Your presence enchants all who surround you
Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol
Now that I've fallen for you, what am I to do?
Sajna kya aavan kol
My love, can I come a little closer?
verse

Kinnu poochaa mein
Who should I turn to?
Esaas kithay rakhday ne, Gallan taalday, Te naal kevain, Hassday ne
How do they conceal their feelings, chatting and laughing as if unburdened?
Chad ditti mei umeedaan saari dunya ton
Hope has deserted me, leaving me empty
Aiwein lokaan diyaan gallan ich phassday ne
We're often trapped by others words without reason
verse

Nai Mei ni bol diyaan jhoot, meray te tera ay suroor
I don't deceive; your allure overwhelms me
Teray uttay likhan ganay sonay jajjday ne
The songs I write are odes to you
Dilaan dee yaari saadi, ve dilaan da nayyo ae kasoor
The connection of our hearts is not a fault of our hearts
Naal rehna si zaroor, saaday thay iraaday
Our desire was simply to be together
verse

Mera koye hor nai ae dass ditta dunya nu
I have made it known to the world you are the only one for me
Jaddon vi aavay apne naal lavay khushian nu
When you come to me happiness follows
Jaddon v door javay, Jaan saadi kadd javay
When you depart, a void engulfs me
Sajna ay teray kol vassna e chaavay
I yearn to stay with you, my love
verse

Muskura ke lay litti ay saadi zimevaari
With a smile, I've assumed all obligations
Ni mein nai kitti kaddi vi teray ton badgumaani
I have never doubted you
Tu mera yaar si, dil aasmaan paar si
When you were by my side, my heart soared across the skies
Ae dou dillaan da pyaar si o
Such was the connection of two hearts
Pyaar na si kaghazi par
Our love speaks beyond words on paper
pre-chorus

Meri khaahish ay toon
You are my enchantment
Meri hasrat ay toon
You alone are my yearning
Assi teray utthay marday ne manday nai kyun
Don't you see, I'd die for you, why won't you hear me?
chorus

Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday
With each day, my longing for you grows
Teray husn uttay marday assi roz
Each day, your beauty leaves me more undone
Ki kariye sajna bol
Tell me how to survive, my love
chorus

Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray
Your presence enchants all who surround you
Teray pyaar ich kariye ki
I want to love you
Hun bol Sajna kya aavan kol
Hun bol sajna kya aavan kol
bridge

Tere te mein waari jaavaan
I dedicate my life to you
Tere gunn gaavaan mein
How I sing your praises
Tere bin jee lagda nay ae
Without you, my heart is numb
Bus tenu chavaan mein
All I want is to have you
Hun raava mor
Turn around for me, won't you
chorus

Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday
With each day, my longing for you grows
Teray husn uttay marday assi roz
Each day, your beauty leaves me more undone
Ki kariye sajna bol
Tell me how to survive, my love
chorus

Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray
Your presence enchants all who surround you
Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol
Now that I've fallen for you, what am I to do?
Sajna kya aavan kol
My love, can I come a little close
